_sText:
New update for my CS:S Map, vs_ninestreet
Updates:
  • Added skybox.
  • Added ambient and misc sounds.
  • Fixed the APC bug. "You can't walk on APC now." 
  • Fixed lighting problems. 
  • Deleted some trees for make map more desert looking. 
  • Added burning oil drums. 
  • Added flashlight. (mp_flashlight 1)
  • Removed some decals. 
  • Deleted grass because of lighting glitch.
  • Fixed doors. 
  • Added lamps to inside of rooms.
If you want to play early version, you can find it in my maps. 
Thanks for playing.
